# Changelog Maintenance

When you make a **major change** to the Obsidion Training Hub, append an entry to `CHANGELOG.md` at the project root.

## What counts as a major change

- Adding, removing, or renaming a route/page
- Creating or restructuring a content section
- Adding or removing a feature (role selection, progress tracking, etc.)
- Changing the data model or registry structure
- Adding new dependencies

Minor fixes (typos, style tweaks, lint fixes) do not need changelog entries.

## Entry format

```markdown
## [YYYY-MM-DD] — Short Summary

### Added / Changed / Removed / Fixed

- Bullet describing what changed and why
```

Place new entries directly below the `---` separator after the file header, above older entries (newest first).
